    ChangeSetReader

    Team Foundation change log writer.

    JenkinsEventNotifier
    This class sends Jenkins events to all "connected" team collections.
    PullRequestParameterAction
    Action that adds the pull request merge event args to the build information.

    Captures the details of the TFS/Team Services build which triggered us.

    TeamGlobalStatusAction
    Added to the build when triggered by TFS/Team Services AND the "Enable Team Status for all jobs" option was enabled.
    TeamGlobalStatusPoster
    Posts the status to TFS/Team Services if the TeamGlobalStatusAction was contributed.

    All the settings that apply globally.

    TeamPullRequestMergedDetailsAction
    Captures details of the TFS/Team Services pull request event which triggered us.
    TeamPushCause

    TeamPushTrigger
    Triggers a build when we receive a TFS/Team Services Git code push event.
    TeamPushTrigger.DescriptorImpl
    This class extends trigger descriptor class.
    TeamResultsAction
    Added by TeamCollectResultsPostBuildAction to enable the download of the ZIP file containing the collected results from the build.
